    std::vector<int> numbers(2, 0);

    for (int i = 0; i < numbers.size(); i++) {
        std::cout << numbers[i] << " ";
    }
    return 0;
}
```
This command will display the output of the `lines` command for the file "example.cpp" in the given repository.

